site_name:
1-15 Bournemouth Road And 143-147 Rye Lane
London
SE15 4ST
description: Demolition of existing buildings at 1-15 (odd) Bournemouth Road and erection of an 8 storey for residential use to provide 55 dwellings [comprising 13 one-bedroom, 39 two-bedroom and 3 three-bedroom flats] together with refurbishment and alterations to 143-147 Rye Lane to provide 7 dwellings [comprising 1 one-bedroom, 4 two-bedroom and 2 three-bedroom flats] on the upper floors together with formation of a roof terrace and continued retail use of the ground floor.
